  "detailed_description": "Experience the fantasy world of Grandura through different types of game modes.<br>You can treat each game mode as its own thing! You don't need to play in any specific order and you don't need to play one in order to enjoy another!<br><br>The Book of Murak, an auto battler set in the desert city of Suksamad. Build your team of monsters, choose which stat and ability to upgrade as they level and equip them items found in the rich market of the city.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371310/extras/6265aa704150ca402080fe953c776897.poster.avif?t=1734395852\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371310/extras/6265aa704150ca402080fe953c776897.webm?t=1734395852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371310/extras/6265aa704150ca402080fe953c776897.mp4?t=1734395852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The Book of Morphus, a traditional roguelike that provides tactical turn-based combat. Do quests, take in a pet, level up, explore dense forests, caves and ruins as a polymorphic creature with the risk of permadeath.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371310/extras/eeec12796f24b31f37ea08ebfe8b35a0.poster.avif?t=1734395852\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371310/extras/eeec12796f24b31f37ea08ebfe8b35a0.webm?t=1734395852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371310/extras/eeec12796f24b31f37ea08ebfe8b35a0.mp4?t=1734395852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The Book of Yohanne, a tower defense where you are also an active unit. Journey through Grandura, fight corrupted horde of enemies and reach the Unholy Sanctum where Dark Incarnate resides. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371310/extras/de63301acf605900fe524143c5c4166b.poster.avif?t=1734395852\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371310/extras/de63301acf605900fe524143c5c4166b.webm?t=1734395852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371310/extras/de63301acf605900fe524143c5c4166b.mp4?t=1734395852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Experience the fantasy world of Grandura through different types of game modes.<br>You can treat each game mode as its own thing! You don't need to play in any specific order and you don't need to play one in order to enjoy another!<br><br>The Book of Murak, an auto battler set in the desert city of Suksamad. Build your team of monsters, choose which stat and ability to upgrade as they level and equip them items found in the rich market of the city.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371310/extras/6265aa704150ca402080fe953c776897.poster.avif?t=1734395852\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371310/extras/6265aa704150ca402080fe953c776897.webm?t=1734395852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371310/extras/6265aa704150ca402080fe953c776897.mp4?t=1734395852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The Book of Morphus, a traditional roguelike that provides tactical turn-based combat. Do quests, take in a pet, level up, explore dense forests, caves and ruins as a polymorphic creature with the risk of permadeath.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371310/extras/eeec12796f24b31f37ea08ebfe8b35a0.poster.avif?t=1734395852\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371310/extras/eeec12796f24b31f37ea08ebfe8b35a0.webm?t=1734395852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371310/extras/eeec12796f24b31f37ea08ebfe8b35a0.mp4?t=1734395852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The Book of Yohanne, a tower defense where you are also an active unit. Journey through Grandura, fight corrupted horde of enemies and reach the Unholy Sanctum where Dark Incarnate resides. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371310/extras/de63301acf605900fe524143c5c4166b.poster.avif?t=1734395852\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371310/extras/de63301acf605900fe524143c5c4166b.webm?t=1734395852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371310/extras/de63301acf605900fe524143c5c4166b.mp4?t=1734395852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
